Payment Arrangement Payment Basis Code
F = Full time payees; P = Part time payees; C = Casual payees; L = Labour hire payees; S = Pension or Annuity payees
The basis of payment indicates the type of arrangement between the payer and payee.
Payment Arrangement Termination Code

When a payment arrangement relationship between two parties has terminated before the declaration/relationship has been reported to the ATO this field must be set to T. In all other cases it is to be set to blank.
Indication of the termination of the payer/payee relationship before the declaration/relationship has been reported to the ATO.
